Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:03:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates  who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after \NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves \Ncaught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and involved in an all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am the only one who you want to kill, \Nplease do not harm the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:04:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Yowahoshi! I told her to stick with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you to save \Nmy beloved Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:10.42,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Hurry up, Luffy! Shirahoshi's \NLife in Jeopardy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Noah is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah is turning away. It's \Nnot gonna crash into the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama saved us \Nby drawing the ship away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess Shirahoshi!\N--Please escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Shirahoshi? \NThere's no way for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go out to the sea in order \Nto keep the Noah away from the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bubble can't take any more damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the main entrance is too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am correct, Luffy-sama's friends were \Nthe last ones who left the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe the gateway is still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Isn't there anything that we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our princess is risking \Nher life to save us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not her fault that Decken is after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is Decken on that ship but now \NHordy is climbing aboard one of the chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He betrayed me, that lunatic - Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he can still be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful for Hordy, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Men are way stronger \Nthan humans in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let him pierce the \Nbubble and go out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it carefully - \Nnot too strong, not too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armee de L'Air Assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gum Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a big chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in between the bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy! He's still under the bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have stop it! We only have \Nto slow it down a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before it catches up with Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pull!\N--Don't let the Noah go any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama! Get somewhere safe \Nwhile we're slowing it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be out of their minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't move it even a millimeter! \NHow senseless is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of cowards like you guys, humans \Nthink they can make fools of Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lives mean nothing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you just keep bringing \Nshame to Fish-Men. Drop dead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama, escape! H-Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right! The entrance \Nto the palace was left open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stay with me! Damn Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi is going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...out to sea through the gateway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Noah is going after her!\N--Princess-sama, go farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How inconvenient it must be to be a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all act so tough on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you couldn't even win a fight \Nwith a Fish-Man child in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how weak you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret standing against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans become powerless in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for a Fish-Man like me, this is where I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can use my true ability to the full extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very fortunate for me \Nthat Shirahoshi went out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:12:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruit eaters fare no better than \Nordinary people in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it ironic, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic and powerless! \NThat's how you truly are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how big you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humans can't even breathe in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, a piece of trash like you \Nwill never become the ruler of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to regret what \Nyou did and beg for mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even do that now, can \Nyou? You pathetic, lowly creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rot in hell, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid hanger-on - \Nwhat a useless gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have stop it! We only have \Nto slow it down a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before it catches up with Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pull!\N--Don't let the Noah go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama! Get somewhere safe \Nwhile we're slowing it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In order to save the people \Nof the Ryugu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to draw the Noah \Naway from the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as far as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like your freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have those \Nwalls of the Hard Shell
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower that were protecting \Nyou for last 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a choice of bleeding to death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or being crushed by the giant ship - Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one last chance, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say "Yes," I'll spare your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have mercy, Decken-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead and live in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my beloved wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let her marry a guy like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our only baby sister! We're \Nnot gonna let you hurt her, Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Mamboshi-sama! Brother \NRyuboshi-sama! Hoe-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not your brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers-sama! Some people at the \Nplaza tried to save me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi! Don't cry now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Brother-sama got mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Father, we can't even \Nlet the ship get damaged-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to return it to the seafloor \Nwithout letting it hit anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! In any case, you shouldn't swim \Nnear undersea mountains or trenches!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah will get damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where should I go, \NBrother Mamboshi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go up! There are too many \Nobstacles down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go beat Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never get away from the Noah \Nand my unending love, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got hurt before - are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the royal family, soldiers, \Ncitizens... all of them got hurt or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even Shirahoshi is trying so hard \Nto save the Ryugu Kingdom while injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is not the time for me to \Nsuffer from such minor injuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merfolk are the greatest \Nswimmers in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, they look like stop motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dead once it hits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I chop both of you up and \Nfeed you to the little fishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate with a 400 million bounty \Nand the prince of the Ryugu Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exquisite food for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although his power is phony, he's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty strong in the \Nsea! Almost like Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to be \Nimpressed at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you go, you can't get \Naway from the Shark Slicer's blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to escape in the cloud of dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shirahoshi!\N--Hey, go to the deck of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you wanted to \Nask me before? But why there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what Jimbei told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the ship is \Nfilled with water, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know but I know Decken \Nis a Devil Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there must be air for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easier for me to fight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna kick the crap out of Hordy \Nand the guy who throws things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Yowahoshi when we left the \Ntower, that I was gonna protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of promises...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We three will become great \Nwarriors like our father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and protect Shirahoshi with \Nour lives as we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a promise to keep too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were defeated by that cheap \Nhoodlum who relies on some
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fake power from the Energy Steroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that we suspected you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. Take me to the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go to the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care of Straw Hat anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is something that \Nneeds to be done right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go after him already!\N--No, wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy has an advantage in the \Nwater since he is a Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If nothing is done...\N--What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go up! Go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's no use, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as my Mark-Mark Curse is in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no way for you \Nto get away from the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hordy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Neptune? Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tormenting Shirahoshi with the Noah now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy suddenly attacks Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His terrifying plan was to \Ndestroy Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy then attacks Shirahoshi \Nto complete his ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Luffy's new attack \Nis unleashed on Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fierce Fight Begins! Luffy vs. Hordy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
